{"tid":2021635,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Ubisoft神秘未公佈超巨型系列新作","createTime":"2020-05-18T00:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T03:05:05.000Z","uid":33359,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c61d7e1cf7ba821619453c45fe2c96bef9235414","tid":2021635,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:31:26.000Z","msg":"※ [本文轉錄自 XBOX 看板 #1UmIGBDl ]<br />\n<br />\n作者: TaipeiKindom (台北金盾) 看板: XBOX<br />\n標題: [情報] Ubisoft神秘未公佈超巨型系列新作<br />\n時間: Sun May 17 19:46:16 2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.trueachievements.com/n41808/ubisoft-unannounced-aaa-game\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trueachievements.com%2Fn41808%2Fubisoft-unannounced-aaa-game&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCVLtzFpi4hzjoOYPfLz2gO4%3D&h=c1ae2cef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.trueachievements.com/n41808/ubisoft-unannounced-aaa-game</a><br />\n<br />\nUbisoft公佈了這個財報年（從現在到明年三月）預定發售的新作，<br />\n其中已經發表的有《刺客教條：英靈殿》、《看門狗：自由軍團》、<br />\n《虹彩六號：隔離禁區》以及新IP《眾神與怪獸》。<br />\n<br />\n這幾款都是三A等級的大作，除此之外，從Ubisoft的名單上，還列了<br />\n一款尚未公佈的、同樣是三A等級的、旗下知名系列的續作。<br />\n<br />\n因為是列在該名單上，所以這款尚未公佈的大作已排定在這個財報<br />\n年上市。<br />\n<br />\n外界揣測這款續作會是那個系列：<br />\n<br />\n1.縱橫諜海：這系列的呼聲最高，上一款是2013年的《縱橫諜海：黑名單》<br />\n<br />\n2.極地戰壕：這系列也有可能是候選之一，距離上一款《極地戰壕5》<br />\n到目前已經隔了長達兩年之久<br />\n<br />\n3.雷曼超人：雷曼也很久沒有出續作，上一款是2013年的《雷曼傳奇》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUbisoft在7月12日將舉辦一場追悼E3的廣告大會，到時應該會<br />\n揭開這款未公佈的3A續作的神秘面紗"},{"pid":"68e42c089a6ac23edbc0bb54320bf6cb890d03f6","tid":2021635,"uid":3545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:32:19.000Z","msg":"係咪beyond good and evil 2呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a68dd75d2ee664e1a5d336740980c32b379631","tid":2021635,"uid":285514,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T00:32:34.000Z","msg":"直接出個<strong>《BUG》</strong>出嚟俾大家玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3d17f940146133c646b3063f